# HireHub Onboarding Portal - Environment Variables
# No environment variables are required for this application.
# All configuration is handled client-side.

# =============================================================
# LOCAL STORAGE KEYS (for reference, not environment variables)
# =============================================================
# HIREHUB_ONBOARDING_PROGRESS - Stores the user's current onboarding step and completion status
# HIREHUB_USER_PROFILE - Stores the user's profile information entered during onboarding
# HIREHUB_THEME_PREFERENCE - Stores the user's selected theme (light/dark)

# =============================================================
# SESSION STORAGE KEYS (for reference, not environment variables)
# =============================================================
# HIREHUB_SESSION_TOKEN - Stores the current session identifier
# HIREHUB_FORM_DRAFT - Stores unsaved form data to prevent loss on page refresh

# =============================================================
# OPTIONAL VITE ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES
# =============================================================
# If you need to configure API endpoints or feature flags in the future,
# add them below prefixed with VITE_ so Vite exposes them to the client.
#
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3000/api
# VITE_ENABLE_ANALYTICS=false